com.google.gwt.file.client

Class File

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • com.google.gwt.file.client.Blob
        • com.google.gwt.file.client.File

  • public class File
extends Blob
    This interface describes a single file in a FileList and exposes its name. It inherits from Blob.

    See http://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/FileAPI/#dfn-File

    Author:
    jarrod
